        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文将讲述<font color="#1E90FF">搭建博客</font>以及<font color="#1E90FF">编写博文</font>一系列步骤。</p><a id="more"></a><p>文章会不定时进行更新，不过我比较懒呐~<br>但是很高兴你阅读我的博文。</p><p>文章可能会涉及有关参考资料、教程、链接如有侵权请联系我删除！</p><hr><p><strong><font color="red" size="4">【博客搭建】</font></strong></p><p>  首先电脑安装必备软件</p><ul><li>Node.js  (<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a>)</li><li>git      (<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a>)</li></ul><p>摸个鱼，双手奉上大佬安装视频 (<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av44544186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av44544186</a>)</p><hr><p>  <strong><font color="red" size="4">【01】博客插入图片</font></strong></p><!--  ![图片插入](https://www.jiligame.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/44e48d14d6ffdabd882985f2d0e0191d.jpg)  -->  <p>  <img src="images/1.png" alt="图片插入"></p>]]></content>
      
      
